    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything i spent twenty years on... it was all based on a mistake. the data was flawed from the start. it's not just a setback, it's like the last two decades of my life just... never happened. i'm just a fraud sitting in an empty office. there's no point in trying to fix it. there's just nothing left.",
